  "iso_27001_definition": {
    "official_text": "Controls should be implemented to ensure that information and information systems can be accessed and used by authorized users in a controlled manner. Control implementations should include but not be limited to: technical measures to protect against physical and logical unauthorized access, and measures to secure information when the systems are not in use.",
