      "Endpoint devices inventory maintained",
      "Risk assessment of endpoints completed",
      "Technical controls implemented",
      "Encryption deployed on devices",
      "Antivirus and antimalware protection",
      "Configuration management baseline",
      "Access controls enforced",
      "Monitoring and logging enabled",
      "Personnel trained on secure use",
      "Physical security controls implemented"
    ]
  },
